{"tid":343977,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[Switch] Splatoon2 [10] 第一頁有Q&A同攻略 點解無人開POST","createTime":"2017-08-02T02:22:06.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-02T06:23:58.000Z","uid":131041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e724ca5fd79174a58d9ae0c65b18fdbf210ff624","tid":343977,"uid":131041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T02:22:06.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://www.nintendo.com.hk/software/switch/img/panel_splatoon2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.nintendo.com.hk%2Fsoftware%2Fswitch%2Fimg%2Fpanel_splatoon2.png&h=19230c2b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>Splatoon<span style=\"color: red;\">2</span>  (スプラトゥーン<span style=\"color: red;\">2</span>)</strong></span><br />\n遊戲/Amiibo/JoyCon/ProController 發售日期：2017-7-21<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DEIEud6XoAAg-Xk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDEIEud6XoAAg-Xk.jpg&h=c9c49d45&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DA6zFx3XgAAoJCJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDA6zFx3XgAAoJCJ.jpg&h=dea22259&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nSplatoon是一款4對4 第三人稱射擊遊戲，與其他射擊遊戲有所不同<br />\n玩家需利用武器把地面塗色，佔色面積較多的一方獲勝 <br />\n<br />\n官方介紹片段(中文):<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=CROuiq-YjlI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DCROuiq-YjlI&d=HBOHLZMEKGqIYX07tum%2BN8P%2FddU7lKBqZb2OVh9Tir8%3D&h=889674b6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=CROuiq-YjlI</a><br />\n<br />\n日本官方網站:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.nintendo.co.jp/switch/aab6a\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nintendo.co.jp%2Fswitch%2Faab6a&d=HBOHLZMEKGqIYX07tum%2BN8P%2FddU7lKBqZb2OVh9Tir8%3D&h=d10f5188\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.nintendo.co.jp/switch/aab6a</a><br />\n<br />\n日本官方Twitter:<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/splatoonjp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsplatoonjp&d=HBOHLZMEKGqIYX07tum%2BN8P%2FddU7lKBqZb2OVh9Tir8%3D&h=b896afd1\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/splatoonjp</a><br />\n<br />\n香港官方網站/ 遊戲介紹:<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.nintendo.com.hk/splatoon2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.nintendo.com.hk%2Fsplatoon2&d=HBOHLZMEKGqIYX07tum%2BN8P%2FddU7lKBqZb2OVh9Tir8%3D&h=0e35aa23\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.nintendo.com.hk/splatoon2</a><br />\n<br />\n歐美官方網站:<br />\n<a href=\"http://splatoon.nintendo.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsplatoon.nintendo.com&d=HBOHLZMEKGqIYX07tum%2BN8P%2FddU7lKBqZb2OVh9Tir8%3D&h=f3c65da8\" target=\"_blank\">http://splatoon.nintendo.com</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>現時會出現的場地 </strong></span></span><br />\n(8揀2, 每2小時轉一次)<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DFFhzlVUAAAXCEg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDFFhzlVUAAAXCEg.jpg&h=72a98bf9&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n開Post用文件<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/175OIz8UWwDI9a-EnViwmLsYUFLQItTDExKSuVRMTpdc/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fdocument%2Fd%2F175OIz8UWwDI9a-EnViwmLsYUFLQItTDExKSuVRMTpdc%2F&d=HBOHLZMEKGqIYX07tum%2BN8P%2FddU7lKBqZb2OVh9Tir8%3D&h=38f373ab\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/document/d/175OIz8UWwDI9a-EnViwmLsYUFLQItTDExKSuVRMTpdc/</a>"},{"pid":"276aa5d79d6817d13da42db11b5860f0770a02a8","tid":343977,"uid":131041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T02:22:29.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">常見問題/ Q&amp;A:</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\nQ: 行日歐美版有咩分別?<br />\n<br />\nA: <br />\n行/日版 遊戲語言為<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>日</strong></span>文 Fes主題跟日ser<br />\n歐澳版 遊戲語言為<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>英</strong></span>文 Fes主題跟歐ser<br />\n美版 遊戲語言為<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>英</strong></span>文 Fes主題跟美ser<br />\n注意Fes活動跟據過住經驗開24小時 故不需擔心時差問題<br />\n<br />\nQ: 點解分咁多版?<br />\nA: 因為唔同版本活動Fes主題有唔同, 例如 午後紅茶, 變型金剛等<br />\n<br />\nQ: <span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>玩唔到網絡對戰</strong></span>?<br />\nA: 港服未開, 去<a href=\"https://accounts.nintendo.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faccounts.nintendo.com&d=HBOHLZMEKGqIYX07tum%2BN8P%2FddU7lKBqZb2OVh9Tir8%3D&h=bb6ee06a\" target=\"_blank\">https://accounts.nintendo.com</a>轉region做日本/美國/歐洲, 之後重新開機<br />\n或者加多個profile, 登入日本/美國/歐洲ac, 再用該profile開game<br />\n<br />\n注: 未知2018年收費服務係跟ac定跟機, 請考慮清楚<br />\n<br />\nQ: 咁唔同版本可唔可以連機?<br />\nA: 平時網絡對戰可以, Fes活動唔得, Local面連可以<br />\n<br />\nQ: 同Nintendo Switch Online App有咩連動?<br />\nA: 可以用App 開房 generate URL, Share URL俾其他人就可以join你<br />\n亦可<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">查看自己對戰之相關數據, 購買遊戲內之服裝</span></strong>, 以及進行語音通話<br />\n由於港服未開 iOS要用美/日ac search &quot;Nintendo Switch Online&quot; download<br />\nAndroid可用apk, download link: <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.apkmirror.com/apk/nintendo-co-ltd/nintendo-switch-online/nintendo-switch-online-1-0-4-release/nintendo-switch-online-1-0-4-android-apk-download/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.apkmirror.com%2Fapk%2Fnintendo-co-ltd%2Fnintendo-switch-online%2Fnintendo-switch-online-1-0-4-release%2Fnintendo-switch-online-1-0-4-android-apk-download%2F&d=HBOHLZMEKGqIYX07tum%2BN8P%2FddU7lKBqZb2OVh9Tir8%3D&h=c5966101\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.apkmirror.com/apk/nintendo-co-ltd/nintendo-switch-online/nintendo-switch-online-1-0-4-release/nintendo-switch-online-1-0-4-android-apk-download/</a><br />\n<br />\nQ: 點<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>用App買衫</strong></span>?<br />\nA: Online對戰一次&gt;開App揀Splatoon2&gt;右上角Shop Icon&gt;揀衫落注文(落訂)&gt;入Game對戰屋(Lobby)隔離<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>海膽仔</strong></span>&gt;最後一個選項俾錢拎衫<br />\n<br />\nQ: <span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>用App訂衫</strong></span>有無限幾時俾錢?<br />\nA: 好似無(?)<br />\n<br />\nQ: 點解衫分咁多牌子?<br />\nA: 各牌子對應一種服裝技能, 抽中該技能的機會 會有所提升<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/aJmum.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FaJmum.jpg&h=e6c60452&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nQ: 隻<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">海膽仔</span></strong>咁多選項其實講緊乜?<br />\nA: 圖片來源: 巴哈 <a href=\"https://forum.gamer.com.tw/C.php?bsn=26487&amp;snA=171&amp;s_author=fanboy1016\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforum.gamer.com.tw%2FC.php%3Fbsn%3D26487%26snA%3D171%26s_author%3Dfanboy1016&d=HBOHLZMEKGqIYX07tum%2BN8P%2FddU7lKBqZb2OVh9Tir8%3D&h=c23039de\" target=\"_blank\">https://forum.gamer.com.tw/C.php?bsn=26487&amp;snA=171&amp;s_author=fanboy1016</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/XZLW6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FXZLW6.jpg&h=c564e157&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\nQ: <span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>Amiibo</strong></span>有咩用?<br />\nA: 可以解鎖衫,武器,歌等, 亦可儲存裝備配置 同埋可以進入影相模式<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DFCqcd1XkAAL4eb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDFCqcd1XkAAL4eb.jpg&h=43dcf688&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nQ: 點解scan Amiibo得個頭拎? 唔係有全身裝咩?<br />\nA: 先對戰超過20場&gt; X掣&gt; +掣&gt; Aamiibo讀自己裝備&gt;去Amiibo Bbox拎其他裝備<br />\n<br />\nQ: amiibo可唔可借比人用<br />\nA: 可以，但要係主機設定還原隻amiibo洗走所有資料，建議拎曬衫先借比人。<br />\n<br />\nQ: 可唔可以唔用<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>體感</strong></span>?<br />\nA: 入設定可以set唔用, 但真心建議俾次機會體感, 上手後自然同方便好多, <br />\n注意體感係for你微調, 大幅轉視角依然係靠右菇, <br />\n<br />\nQ: 可唔可以set手提mode唔用體感, 桌上mode同TV mode用體感?<br />\nA: 可以, 手提同桌上&amp;TV mode係分開set<br />\n<br />\nQ: 對戰時點<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>傳送去隊友度</strong></span>?<br />\nA: X -&gt; 揀隊友 -&gt; A<br />\n<br />\nQ: 點出<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>大絕</strong></span>?<br />\nA: 右上角儲滿氣按R3(右菇)<br />\n<br />\nQ: 武器隔離枝旗仔代表咩?<br />\nA: 熟練度, 到5嘅倍數會有Bonus經驗值<br />\n<br />\nQ: 有無需要買Pro手掣?<br />\nA: Pro手掣舒服好多但唔係必需<br />\n<br />\nQ: 視角怪怪地喎....?<br />\nA: Y掣Reset 視角<br />\n<br />\nQ: 點<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>畫畫</strong></span>?<br />\nA: 主城紅色郵筒<br />\n<br />\nQ: Hero Mode (<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>單人劇情模式</strong></span>) 點入?<br />\nA: 主城左上拎遮個「啊婆」<br />\n<br />\nQ: Hero Mode d武器點升? 包唔包埋對戰mode?<br />\nA: 第一關門口個box。兩個mode嘅武器係分開<br />\n<br />\nQ: <span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>Salmon Run</strong></span> 點先有得online玩?<br />\nA: 指定時間(X掣-&gt;ステージ情報-&gt;Salmon Run有得睇,顯示時間係你本地時間)<br />\n去左上商會, 或者直接 X-&gt;商會<br />\n<br />\nQ: <span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>Salmon Run </strong></span>Mode奬品去邊度兌換?<br />\nA: 主城左上角市商會隔黎有部機<br />\n<br />\nQ: 點同FD一齊玩<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>Salmon Run</strong></span> Mode?<br />\nA: Salmon Run Mode介面揀第二個開房, 叫FD揀第二個揀你個人仔入你間房, 齊人後開場, 唔夠4個人會幫你揾街外人入來<br />\n<br />\nQ: 有無得<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>一機雙打</strong></span>?<br />\nA: 無<br />\n<br />\nQ: 邊度開<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>本地(Local)對戰</strong></span>場?<br />\nA: 去機鋪(イカッチャ, 主城右面), 第一個係揾房, 第二個係開房, 第三個係開Salmon Run 房<br />\n<br />\nQ: 一開Game叫你Set個性別同造型之後仲有無得換?<br />\nA: 主城撳X-&gt;R R R-&gt;最底(その他)-&gt;最底(プレイヤー設定)<br />\n<br />\nQ: 點用倍經/倍$卷?<br />\nA: 主城黃巴士<br />\n<br />\nQ: 有無連登Splatoon交友(<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>加朋友</strong></span>)區?<br />\nA: 有,<br />\n連登 Splatoon2 任豚登記表<br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/cVBZKp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FcVBZKp&d=HBOHLZMEKGqIYX07tum%2BN8P%2FddU7lKBqZb2OVh9Tir8%3D&h=ea55f124\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/cVBZKp</a><br />\n<br />\n連登 Splatoon2 任豚名單<br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/zmzkon\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2Fzmzkon&d=HBOHLZMEKGqIYX07tum%2BN8P%2FddU7lKBqZb2OVh9Tir8%3D&h=9b25da8b\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/zmzkon</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">服裝技能</span></strong>中文翻譯(from 巴哈):<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/7reG7y0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F7reG7y0.png&h=ef4968eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://forum.gamer.com.tw/C.php?bsn=31587&amp;snA=1730\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforum.gamer.com.tw%2FC.php%3Fbsn%3D31587%26snA%3D1730&d=HBOHLZMEKGqIYX07tum%2BN8P%2FddU7lKBqZb2OVh9Tir8%3D&h=426fa200\" target=\"_blank\">https://forum.gamer.com.tw/C.php?bsn=31587&amp;snA=1730</a>"},{"pid":"278f376624689a22f4caec7d96d8d94484cdbc0d","tid":343977,"uid":33206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T02:22:46.000Z","msg":"Splatoon fest!"},{"pid":"c261e0d384a2ff1510b99c575c87a83b29188548","tid":343977,"uid":131041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T02:22:48.000Z","msg":"Q: <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">Rank Mode (ガチマッチ) </span></strong>啲玩法係點架?<br />\nA: Rank mode有3款，三款各自有獨立ranking，都係由C-開始<br />\n<br />\n1. <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">運魚</span></strong>:地圖中央有枝魚炮，射爆佢個保護罩，就可以拎枝魚炮上身，自己武器就變成魚炮，魚炮可以儲力，將魚炮運去敵方陣地的小高台就嬴 (通常係重生點行出少少的位置)<br />\n畫面上方的數字係魚炮曾經運到有幾近小高台<br />\n有人拎起枝魚炮，畫面會有show個icon仔話你知條友係邊<br />\n敵方射爆保護罩爆開會死人，見到就爆唔好行咁近，邊隊射爆保護罩都可以搶拎魚炮，不過一爆就埋去搶好危險<br />\n<br />\n2. <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">搶地</span></strong>：地圖會有專有地區框起左，將成個框起的地方油到變成自己色就開始count down，count 到0就贏，被對方搶返會有罰秒<br />\n如果有兩個框起地區，要填晒兩個先開始count down<br />\n填完個地安全就留一兩個人，另外一兩個就出去填返對面的移動路線，反兜敵人or埋伏，唔好企死個框區等敵人到<br />\n<br />\n3. <span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>推車/推塔</strong></span>：地圖中央有座塔，企上去就會自動行去敵方陣地，成功去到敵方陣地就贏，雙方都有人企係上面會唔郁<br />\n自方陣地時，企一企上去佢會自動返中央地帶，唔駛死企上面<br />\n越多人企上面行得越快，越易死晒 <strong><div style=\"text-align: right;\"><em>by 景三巴打</em></div></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">Salmon Run教學/相關資訊/武器心得 </span></strong></span><div style=\"text-align: right;\"><strong><em>by 矢作萌花巴打</em></strong></div><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DFOvO9YVYAEfgTp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDFOvO9YVYAEfgTp.jpg&h=1c99678d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1lW9ZS876IwGSLzaLUJoPHF6D-xEdxT6SlHKhzGloadc/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fdocument%2Fd%2F1lW9ZS876IwGSLzaLUJoPHF6D-xEdxT6SlHKhzGloadc%2F&d=HBOHLZMEKGqIYX07tum%2BN8P%2FddU7lKBqZb2OVh9Tir8%3D&h=9474ea7e\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/document/d/1lW9ZS876IwGSLzaLUJoPHF6D-xEdxT6SlHKhzGloadc/</a>"},{"pid":"546468cdb830401ae7fed77195899e2e67264a4a","tid":343977,"uid":131041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T02:23:07.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">裝備選擇心得/入手方法 </span></strong></span><div style=\"text-align: right;\"><strong><em>by 鑫毳巴打</em></strong></div><br />\n<br />\n裝備技能選擇<br />\n<br />\n前提：這是一篇以技能為優先考慮的文章<br />\n<br />\n好多人都會問到底買唔買依件好買唔買個件好<br />\n好似驚死日後買唔到或者唔買就走寶咁<br />\n首先可以諗下依兩樣<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><em>■如何分辦一件裝備是否合適自己？(主屬方面)</em></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n裝備主用途：<br />\n-提高自己生存力<br />\n-發揮武器效能到最大<br />\n-加快自己死亡後回到戰場速度<br />\n-裝飾<br />\n<br />\n[生存力]<br />\n一直生存先可以為整隊持續貢獻<br />\n總好過你油少少死幾百次<br />\n你要知當你油完自己死係會醬爆<br />\n你油過既野同無油過分別唔大<br />\n只要你生存 敵人知你存在 <br />\n就可以牽引住敵人 <br />\n等齊隊友就可以齊齊打開劣勢<br />\n<br />\n你同敵人對射時有無試過無油<br />\n或者覺得自己移位唔夠快補唔到刀/ 避唔到粒子彈？<br />\n要增加生存力，<br />\n第一件事係有能力逃走<br />\n<br />\n要改善依個情況，裝備配答就可以幫到你。<br />\n<br />\n安全鞋：文字上係寫可以減低敵方墨水對自己傷害。<br />\n\t   實際上其實仲有其他用途<br />\n\t   安全鞋可以增加係敵墨上游動距離<br />\n\t   可能你唔知 其實我地係可以游過少量既敵墨<br />\n\t   問題只係潛到一定短暫時間佢會強制性迫你變人型<br />\n\t   游動距離增加  走位更方便 <br />\n   而已安全鞋仲可減少人型時踩上敵墨既速度懲罰<br />\n<br />\n游速：走得快好世界，左閃右閃避彈一流。<br />\n<br />\n回油/減主耗：戰場上無子彈你同等死無咩分別。<br />\n保持住有一定彈藥數 對生存總有幫助<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n[武器效能]<br />\n裝備能力加乘可以最大化武器既長處<br />\n<br />\n機槍：人型移速可以大大增加油地範圍<br />\n\t<br />\n狙擊：人型可以從牆邊快速移動突擊<br />\n<br />\nRoller：游速可以神速走位見一個殺一個<br />\n<br />\n所有炸彈副武：炸彈可以擾亂敵人仲可以索敵用<br />\n\t\t 適當地運用對戰鬥有一定幫助<br />\n\t\t上代3.3減副耗仲可以二連炸擊(今代未清楚)<br />\n\t\t配上大技可以回油功能 四連炸彈都可以玩死好多人<br />\n<br />\n[復帰速度]<br />\n死得快番上戰場時間越短越好唔洗教啦<br />\n<br />\nカムバック（Comeback）<br />\n死亡時重生有３０秒所有能力上升<br />\n提升兩個主屬游速左右<br />\n配上一兩個游速你會飛天<br />\n<br />\nSuperJump+StealthJump<br />\n跳加速+隱跳<br />\n留意跳落地個下如果敵人近既照樣會見到你落地點<br />\n你會曝路隊友潛伏位置害死佢<br />\n所以千萬不要飛交戰中既隊友<br />\n<br />\n[強迫症]<br />\n你會想買晒所有野<br />\n但你有錢嗎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n■裝備入手方法<br />\n-商店<br />\n-老任App商店<br />\n-廣場上注文(Order)<br />\n-Amiibo<br />\n<br />\n每一個裝備都會有個牌子<br />\n而牌子會影響小技能出現機率<br />\n詳情可望下依個網<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://game8.jp/splatoon-2/164683\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgame8.jp%2Fsplatoon-2%2F164683&d=HBOHLZMEKGqIYX07tum%2BN8P%2FddU7lKBqZb2OVh9Tir8%3D&h=75ff7978\" target=\"_blank\">https://game8.jp/splatoon-2/164683</a><br />\n小翻譯<br />\n付きやすい：易出現  (每一格30%)<br />\n付きにくい：難出現  (每一格5% )<br />\n目前隻Game出既時間唔長<br />\n所以好多裝備資料同難出既能力都未清楚<br />\n大部份資料都係一代沿用過黎等人測試<br />\n你當參考住先就OK<br />\n表上無既牌子=無傾向<br />\n例如如果想刷多d安全鞋碎片既<br />\n就盡量買多dパトロイカ裝備升<br />\n升完去海膽仔度比兩萬洗<br />\n<br />\n[商店]<br />\n每晚11點更新商品<br />\n會根據你lv有排列唔同<br />\n未夠15lv唔會有3星裝<br />\n到20lv時123星會各有三件<br />\n今日買到聽日唔一定買到<br />\n但你唔買就九成聽日都會見到佢仲係度<br />\n<br />\n[老任App商店]<br />\n限時裝備 會跟遊戲商店賣既物品相同<br />\n但主屬會變左另一款<br />\nOrder完可以去搵海膽仔點最低個格拎貨<br />\n留意間唔中三星係會有伏貨<br />\n姐係你根本唔會用既主屬Cover左本來好有用個種<br />\n想查番本身件裝係咩主屬既可以上依個網址<br />\n暫時最齊係佢 但都係唔齊....<br />\n頂住先 話晒新Game修改太多<br />\n<a href=\"https://splatoon2.gamepedia.jp/gears\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsplatoon2.gamepedia.jp%2Fgears&d=HBOHLZMEKGqIYX07tum%2BN8P%2FddU7lKBqZb2OVh9Tir8%3D&h=ca7125fc\" target=\"_blank\">https://splatoon2.gamepedia.jp/gears</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n[注文]<br />\n見到路人啲衫啱心水就同佢傾計落order得架啦<br />\n最好就點d主屬同副屬差唔多既野<br />\n有60%機會會出左1小屬相同 價錢唔記得<br />\n有10%機會會出左2小屬相同 賣5萬<br />\n有1%機會完全相同  賣10萬<br />\n注文點都貴過商店買<br />\n但點都好盡量唔好注品牌貨好注品牌貨<br />\n以下為小弟失敗例子：<a href=\"http://i.imgur.com/a0pqlsl.png\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fa0pqlsl.png&d=HBOHLZMEKGqIYX07tum%2BN8P%2FddU7lKBqZb2OVh9Tir8%3D&h=73785b87\" target=\"_blank\">http://i.imgur.com/a0pqlsl.png</a><br />\n<br />\n[打工]<br />\n當你有當月份裝備<br />\n再打多一件相同裝備時<br />\n無小屬性可換4000蚊<br />\n有小屬性可換碎片<br />\n簡一件岩心水既留起啦<br />\n小屬一定無傾向 刷碎片都唔錯<br />\n<br />\n[Amiibo]<br />\n打完單機Mode<br />\n讀過一次裝備<br />\n再玩多過20場<br />\n就可以拎晒佢成套裝<br />\n無得注。"},{"pid":"5ace170d21089691a50318c6c12edfd34febed21","tid":343977,"uid":303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T02:23:20.000Z","msg":"第11個post啦 重開啦"},{"pid":"e572dc76d50130aa1a7b9d3bbc05a6e6cf815100","tid":343977,"uid":131041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T02:23:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>第11個post啦 重開啦</blockquote><br />\n我錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5c4bd2c8a7fce634de535b30b0bf0616c2263ee","tid":343977,"uid":8659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T02:24:01.000Z","msg":"amiibo肯定唔洗打哂單人mode<br />\n我拎齊果陣只係過完第2版"},{"pid":"65c3912d6c5509aeee6f6a003c4ecac2f3af065d","tid":343977,"uid":131041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T02:25:54.000Z","msg":"lee個開錯左Number, 去lee到啦<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/343983/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/343983/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"b5bef840121c5bfbd96755a1ba410907574abc4d","tid":343977,"uid":30517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T06:23:58.000Z","msg":"點解我成日都起對戰模式見到人拎單機把輕機槍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}